Package org.aslib

package org.aslib
  • Class
    Description
    Admin
    The Admin interface defines administrative actions in the auction service.
    Auction
    The Auction interface defines methods for interacting with an auction.
    AuctionStatus
    The AuctionStatus enum represents the possible states of an auction.
    Item
    The Item class represents an item that can be auctioned.
    Service
    The Service interface defines methods for user login and retrieval of administrative and auction data.
    User
    The User interface defines methods for user interactions such as bidding, claiming items, and managing credits.
